    <li>The exam will be available for 24 hours on Gradescope starting at 12am (PST) on the scheduled date: however, once you start the exam, you will have 65 minutes to finish and submit your exam. The exam is intended to take 50 minutes: the remaining 15 minutes are intended for the scanning and submission of the exam on Gradescope. In particular, we will not accept submissions after the 65 minute deadline: it is your responsibility to submit the exam on time. For example, if you choose to write the exam for 65 minutes and do not leave yourself enough time to scan the exam, then you will not receive credit for the exam.</li>
    <li>As with the quizzes, the 24 hour deadline supersedes your allotted 65 minutes for the exam. For example, if you start the exam at 11:40pm (PST), you will need to submit it within 20 minutes to receive credit since the 24 hour deadline would come before the end of your 65 minutes.</li>
